snippet.title: Zen Pinball - PS3 - My first Game
snippet.description:
Zen Pinball was released today on PSN, Here's my first game..
The Table is "Tesla" and follows a mechanical/clockwork style, Nice extra Preview for anybody wanting to see more after playing the "Shamen" Table on th eDemo...

O.K, so i'm not the biggest fan of Pinball, and i've not played any Pinball game for at least 6 months..
But I Tried
